<chapter condition="TITLE=System Features: Guarantee Maintenance;ACCESS=BA_GU_MA" role="TOPIC">
  <title>Guarantee Maintenance</title>

  <section condition="TITLE=System Features: Guarantee Maintenance" id="BGM"
           role="TOPIC">
    <title>Overview</title>

    <para role="TEXT">A bank administrator can define standard Guarantee
    templates to customers within the <xi:include href="../entities_en.xml"
    xpointer="ent_appli" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" /> to
    assist the in their day to day operations. Guarantees are mainly free form
    documents describing the type and content of the Guarantee. Bankers
    Guarantees are used by customers in the Trade Finance area or the
    portal.</para>

    <para role="TEXT">Selecting this function will display a display a list of
    Existing Guarantee templates.</para>
</section>
    <section role="ITEM">
      <title>Guarantee Maintenance - Guarantee List</title>

      <para role="TEXT">To navigate to the <emphasis role="bold">Guarantee
      Maintenance</emphasis> function, from the toolbar, select
      <emphasis>System Features</emphasis> from the home page, then select
      <emphasis>Guarantee Maintenance</emphasis> from the left side navigation
      menu. A list of all the existing guarantee templates is displayed. You
      can search the list by entering search criteria in the <guilabel
      moreinfo="none">Name</guilabel> fields at the top of the page.</para>

      <para role="TEXT">The Guarantee list has the following
      columns:<informaltable role="TEXT">
          <tgroup cols="2">
            <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="2.0*" />

            <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="8.0*" />

            <thead>
              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para>Field</para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para>Description</para></entry>
              </row>
            </thead>

            <tbody>
              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para> <guilabel
                moreinfo="none">Name</guilabel> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para>The name of the Guarantee
                template.</para></entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para> <guilabel
                moreinfo="none">Type</guilabel> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para>The type of the
                Guarantee.</para></entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para> <guilabel
                moreinfo="none">Associated Customers</guilabel>
                </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para>The customers with access to the
                guarantee template.</para></entry>
              </row>
            </tbody>
          </tgroup>
        </informaltable></para>

      <para role="TEXT">You can modify a Guarantee by clicking the <guiicon
      moreinfo="none">Edit</guiicon> <inlinemediaobject>
          <imageobject>
            <imagedata fileref="../images/icon_edit.gif" role="ICON_EDIT"
                       width="4mm" />
          </imageobject>
        </inlinemediaobject> icon in the right-hand column or delete it by
      clicking the <guibutton moreinfo="none">Delete</guibutton>
      <inlinemediaobject>
          <imageobject>
            <imagedata fileref="../images/icon_trash.gif" role="ICON_TRASH"
                       width="4mm" />
          </imageobject>
        </inlinemediaobject> icon.</para>

      <para role="TEXT">Click the <guibutton moreinfo="none">Add a new
      Guarantee </guibutton>button at the bottom of the list to add a
      Guarantee.</para>

      <section role="ITEM">
